songs.title: Hang Me Up to Dry
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
Oh, hang me up to dry
You wrung me out
Too, too, too many times
Oh, hang me up to dry
Oh, I'm pearly like the whites
The whites of your eyes

[Beatboxing]

[Chorus]
Oh, hang me up to dry
You wrung me out
Too, too, too many times
Oh, hang me up to dry
I'm pearly like the whites
The whites of your eyes
